            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0x820EE2EA<!--String: "Now that we're closer, I'll let you in on a secret: I am Vulfgang Mulder, the author. Not many know. I want to live the quiet life, and I don't want to draw attention to Moonwood Mill, so I keep my real identity secret. "--></T>
                  <T>0x4BD0E321<!--String: "Kristopher believes that when you are in control of your emotions, you are the truest version of yourself. It allows you to act in a way that best represents your personal ideals and motives. It was this philosophy that piqued my interest in the Werewolf lifestyle. I would never had made the change if it wasn't for him. "--></T>
                  <T>0xBF07DEC<!--String: "My favorite moon phase is the Waning Crescent. For Werewolves, it bestows the gift of logic. I find I can read books far faster than during any other moon phase. I can't think of a better way of spending the night! "--></T>
                  <T>0xB39067C8<!--String: "Greg is a living fixture of history, a reminder of darker times, and a warning for those who forget the value of control. He long ago gave into his rage and lost himself in it. It's a sad tale. "--></T>
                  <T>0x8F883A81<!--String: "If I could go back to how things were before I arrived, would I? No. I have a family now. They're my pack."--></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
